metadata.name: MetaFluencer #1
metadata.description: ILONSI AB (publ) has created 1000 MetaFluencer`s to make influencer collaborations aboard smoother, with ambitions of decentralize e-commerce. Each NFT has rights and benefits such as a shop at our marketplace, 5% of the sales at ILONSI Shop, $ILONSI tokens, all rights attached to the Meta Fluencer, invites to parties and join presales for NFT projects by ILONSI AB (publ).
